data.description:
Introducing  a stunning property located in the desirable city of Charlotte, NC This beautiful home is situated in a prime location, offering convenience, comfort, and style.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting interior. The open floor plan connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating space for entertaining guests or spending quality time, The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample storage space, and a center island,
The property boasts 3 bedrooms, including a luxurious master suite. The master bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with its generous size, walk-in closet, and en-suite bathroom, additional 2 Beds Room in upstair. Additional bedrooms are spacious and well-appointed.The backyard also offers a patio or deck area, The vibrant city offers a thriving arts scene and a strong sense of community.With its impressive features, convenient location, and stylish design, this property is sure to exceed your expectations.
